text:
UPDATE: Closed

Hi ya'll!
My team and I are figuring out the reporting and analytics. Does anyone know if there is a way to track a prospect's journey through the webpages? Like where they came from (google search, LinkedIn campaign, etc),  which page they started on and which pages they went to in order before they became a lead?
Thanks so much!

Follow-up question: Can a report show the demographics of the prospects & leads?
Found out HubSpot doesn't have a report for demographics. Your next best option is Google Analytics
